To add pages go to _posts directory.
Name the pages with this format -> 2022-08-26-conv.md. [Date-TitleOfThePage.md] It will pop automatically at the end of the front page.

index.html - this page is the front page.
_config.yml - this page consists of important settings.

_data/navigation.yml - consists of main links for index.html pages. 

hem-chandra.github.io/assets/css/main.scss - to change the URL link

